Copyright (c) 2026 The Blade Authors

This extension was inspired by, and supersedes, the community extension
"BLADE" (publisher id: dhwang, https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=dhwang.blade)
by Daohui Wang (@wangdh15), released under the MIT License. The original
extension demonstrated the task-runner UX for Blade in VS Code. This is a
clean-room reimplementation with a different architecture (blade-as-source-of-
truth via `blade dump`/`query`, the VS Code Tasks API, and BUILD-file language
features); no source code from the original is included, but we gratefully
acknowledge the prior art.
